### List frames (public)
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/photos/frames/available

### Create frame
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/frames
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "name": "2x2 Grid Frame",
  "description": "Created via REST Client",
  "rows": 2,
  "cols": 2,
  "photoWidth": 300,
  "photoHeight": 300,
  "padding": 20,
  "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
  "message": "Smile!"
}

### Get frame by id
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/frames/{{FRAME_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update frame
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/api/frames/{{FRAME_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "name": "Updated Frame Name",
  "description": "Updated via REST Client",
  "rows": 3,
  "cols": 1,
  "photoWidth": 250,
  "photoHeight": 250,
  "padding": 15,
  "backgroundColor": "#f0f0f0",
  "message": "Cheese!"
}

### Delete frame
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/frames/{{FRAME_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

